  "text": "There is well accepted theory showing that some level of diversity is required to achieve the best performance on training data [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . This indicates the role of diversity in stationary learning problems; a set of suitably diverse base learners is required for the ensemble is to be expressive enough to correctly classify more of the training data than a single model.",
